{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grid Areas","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Un <strong>grid area</strong> es una o más <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Cell\">grid cells <small>(en-US)</small></a> que forman un área rectangular en la cuadrícula. Los grid areas se crean cuando se coloca un ítem usando <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">disposición basada en líneas</a> o cuando se definen áreas usando <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">grid areas con nombre</a>.</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/14771/1_Grid_Area.png\" alt=\"Image showing a highlighted grid area\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Las Grid areas <em>deben</em> ser de naturaleza rectangular; no es posible crear, por ejemplo, un grid area en forma de T o L.</p>\n<p>En el siguiente ejemplo, tengo un contenedor de cuadrícula con dos ítems. Los he nombrado con la propiedad <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> y luego los he distribuido en la cuadrícula usando <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code></a>. Esto crea dos áreas de cuadrícula, una que cubre cuatro celdas de la cuadrícula, la otra dos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid #f76707<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff4e6<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid #ffa94d<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffd8a8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #d9480f<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item2</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"ejemplo sample\" id=\"frame_ejemplo\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas/_sample_.ejemplo.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"aprenda_más","title":"Aprenda más","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"referencia_de_propiedad","title":"Referencia de propiedad","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"otras_lecturas","title":"Otras lecturas","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of grid layout</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></em></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#grid-area-concept\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Definition of Grid Areas in the CSS Grid Layout specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Aprenda más","id":"aprenda_más"}],"summary":"Un grid area es una o más grid cells (en-US) que forman un área rectangular en la cuadrícula. Los grid areas se crean cuando se coloca un ítem usando disposición basada en líneas o cuando se definen áreas usando grid areas con nombre.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Zone de grille","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Grid Areas (グリッド領域)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Grid Areas","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/glossary/grid_areas","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/glossary/grid_areas/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Glossary","title":"Glosario"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas","title":"Grid Areas"}],"pageTitle":"Grid Areas - Glosario | MDN","noIndexing":false}}